These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, lily, zinnia
City: new-york, marseilles, hamburg, venice
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, february, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person who growsorchid is the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower    | poppy  | zinnia | lily    | orchid       |
| City         | marseilles | venice    | hamburg      | new-york |
| Birthday   | november   | february | january | september        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, daisy, poppy
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, german, colombian
4 different games are played: poker, chess, bridge, canasta
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the german is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing poker is the australian##1
6. the person playing canasta is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Flower        | daisy   | azalea | zinnia     | poppy      |
| Nationality         | chinese | german | colombian | australian |
| Game   | chess    | canasta   | bridge     | poker      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, emerald, purple, apricot
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, montecristo, davidoff
4 different games are played: chess, monopoly, go, snooker
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes apricot is the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the person who likes orange is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Color         | orange | emerald | purple | apricot |
| Cigar   | davidoff       | siglo    | aristoff | montecristo     |
| Game   | chess | go    | snooker | monopoly    |

