.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
City: edinburgh, hamburg, miami, berlin
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, reading, cooking
There 4 different types of food: corn, cherry, kale, apricot
1. the person traveling to miami is the person eating apricot##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person traveling to miami##1
7. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| City         | edinburgh | berlin | miami | hamburg |
| Hobby       | puzzles     | cooking      | card-games     | reading      |
| Food   | cherry | corn         | apricot      | kale        |

