.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, dancer, firefighter, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, dubstep, rock, classical
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, jet-ski, train
1. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
2. the firefighter is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person driving the van is the fan of rock##1
5. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the project-manager is the fan of dubstep##1
7. the musician is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | firefighter   | musician | dancer  | project-manager      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | jazz        | classical  | dubstep       |
| Transport         | van | jet-ski    | subway | train |

