.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
City: boston, nizza, new-york, miami
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, baking, video-games, cooking
There 4 different types of food: lime, radish, eggplant, zucchini
1. the person traveling to boston is the person eating radish##1
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person traveling to miami is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| City           | nizza | new-york | miami | boston |
| Hobby   | cooking   | video-games  | baking | singing   |
| Food   | zucchini   | lime     | eggplant | radish       |

