.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, canadian, american, british
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, colonial, modern
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, tulip, azalea, iris
1. the colonial house is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growstulip is the american##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the chinese##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
8. the townhouse house is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Nationality          | chinese  | british | american   | canadian     |
| House         | modern | townhouse   | gothic-revival  | colonial |
| Flower   | azalea         | orchid  | tulip | iris  |

