.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, may, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, daisy, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, parkour, cricket
1. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday      | february | may     | july | november |
| Flower   | bellflower  | begonia | daisy       | sunflower    |
| Sport   | skiing   | cricket | tennis    | parkour |

