.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, balloon-flower, lily
4 different pets are kept: goat, rat, cat, snake
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, coral, lilac, apricot
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the person who likes lilac is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower        | lily   | amaryllis  | rose   |
| Pet   | goat         | snake     | rat    | cat       |
| Color         | coral | azure | lilac | apricot |

