.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, cricket, sailing
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, go, snooker
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, car, bike
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person playing go is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
7. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Sport   | basketball    | cricket | sailing | snowboarding        |
| Game       | snooker | chess  | canasta | go     |
| Transport        | tram    | car   | bike  | scooter |

