.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, cat, ferret, guinea-pig
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, german, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, lavender, blood-red, black
1. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
2. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the mexican is on the left of the malaysian##1
4. the dutch is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who likes amber is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the dutch is the person who likes blood-red##1
8. the german is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Pet         | chinchilla  | guinea-pig | cat  | ferret |
| Nationality       | german | mexican        | malaysian | dutch       |
| Color   | amber   | lavender          | black          | blood-red       |

