.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann, blend, prince
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, pink, mauve, orange
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip, dahlia, amaryllis
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes orange is the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
6. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar         | prince   | blend   | tiparillo | dannemann |
| Color   | mauve | amber | pink   | orange |
| Flower   | amaryllis     | lily  | dahlia  | tulip  |

