.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, romance, family, thriller
House: tower, colonial, ranch-style, futuristic
City: hannover, colone, nizza, san-francisco
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is the futuristic house##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the colonial house##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the tower house##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | romance    | western        | family |
| House   | colonial     | ranch-style     | futuristic        | tower   |
| City         | colone   | hannover | nizza | san-francisco  |

