.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, dannemann, vegafina
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, card-games, hiking, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, funk, trance, hip-hop
1. the fan of jazz is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of trance##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar      | tiparillo        | vegafina    | aristoff | dannemann      |
| Hobby   | traveling        | reading   | card-games  | hiking  |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop | funk | trance   | jazz |

