.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, boat, taxi
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, poppy, tulip
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, dancer, scientist, security-guard
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the musician is on the right of the dancer##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the scientist##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the boat##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Transport          | helicopter     | taxi   | boat | motorbike |
| Flower   | bellflower | tulip | poppy | iris   |
| Job           | security-guard    | dancer     | musician      | scientist     |

