.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, adventure, thriller, romance
There 4 different types of food: potato, pear, pineapple, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving, camping, cooking
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
5. the person eating potato is the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
7. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
8. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure  | thriller  | comedy | romance |
| Food   | lemon   | potato | pear   | pineapple      |
| Hobby         | board-games | camping    | skydiving   | cooking         |

 